      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it still looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no spills, just pure driving perfection. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
